snippet.title: POPGOES Evergreen - Updated Gameplay Preview 08/17/2023
snippet.description:
Buy POPGOES Arcade: https://store.steampowered.com/app/19...
Follow POPGOES Evergreen: https://gamejolt.com/games/evergreen/...

Here is another video showcasing an early build of POPGOES Evergreen.
This version of the game has been updated with new features and
visual effects, compared to the version that was shown last week. There are still lots of things to do, but I thought I'd share this
preview so you can see our progress. This is likely the last time I
will present the gameplay in its early state like this.

POPGOES is an official Five Nights at Freddy's spinoff series, developed by Kane Carter and produced/licensed by Scott Cawthon.

#madewithfusion 

Please subscribe to our channel.
